OL,3,CPrestigious school announces
OL,4,Cinvestigation into alleged child abuse
OL,6,FGuernsey's Elizabeth College has
OL,7,Fannounced an external investigation
OL,8,Finto claims of historical child abuse.
OL,10,FThe College says, in recent months, it
OL,11,Fhas received "a number of disclosures
OL,12,Fof alleged non-recent abuse concerning
OL,13,Fthe experiences of former pupils in
OL,14,Fthe 1970s and 1980s".
OL,16,FAn independent, expert review has been
OL,17,Fcommissioned by the College, while
OL,18,FGuernsey Police are encouraging anyone
OL,19,Fwho may be affected to come forward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/2
